<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Interview Preparation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 500px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: blue;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        ul {
            text-align: left;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        button {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to the Mock Interview Preparation</h1>
        <p>Before beginning the mock interview, let's go through some important details:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Total Interview Time:</strong> 1 minutes</li>
            <li><strong>Types of Questions:</strong> Personal, Technical, HR</li>
            <p>Time allocated for  the individual round  is 20s,if the answeing exceeds 20s next question will displayed.Try to answer within that time</p>
        </ul>
        <p>When you're ready, click the "Start Interview" button below to begin. </p><BR>
            ALL THE BEST:)
        <button onclick="startInterview()">Start Interview</button>
    </div>

    <script>
        function startInterview() {
            window.location.href = "/student/fluency";
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
